    "In this way, we focus on two scenarios of application where digital deception is a hot topic by virtue of its devastating implications.",
    "First, in Sect. 5.1, social engineering attacks are presented where fake news generation within social media networks is addressed.",
    "Then, cybersecurity issues found in IoT networks are tackled in Sect. 5.2.",
    "Online social media platforms are crucial for facilitating human interaction and communication.",
    "However, they and other websites which do not have the security safeguards to safeguard this data may make sensitive information accessible."
